- Tu dois te sentir mieux.
- Oui.

96
00:07:54,853 --> 00:07:59,802
J'ai plus de forces.
Je ne suis pas Jonathan, mais je me défends.

97
00:07:59,893 --> 00:08:02,453
Tu continues ou non?

98
00:08:03,293 --> 00:08:05,249
A quoi?

99
00:08:05,333 --> 00:08:08,325
A manger ce concentré de force multicolore?

100
00:08:09,533 --> 00:08:14,084
